### Test Semantic Search - Debug

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@connectionId = YOUR_CONNECTION_ID_HERE

### 1. Check if database is analyzed (schema should exist)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 2. Analyze database first (this will index to Qdrant)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/analyze?mode=overview
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 3. Check overview (should have analysis data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 4. Test semantic search - Vietnamese
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/search?query=khách hàng&limit=10&scoreThreshold=0.5
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 5. Test semantic search - English
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/search?query=customer&limit=10&scoreThreshold=0.5
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 6. Test semantic search - Abbreviation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/search?query=KH&limit=10&scoreThreshold=0.5
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}

### 7. Test semantic search - Concept
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/search?query=sales order&limit=10&scoreThreshold=0.5
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv JWT_TOKEN}}
